@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jdbxpv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v2 = 0.44
    v0 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v2 + 0.22 / tmp + 0.59)))
    v2 = (v1 - 0.86)
    tmp = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.75 - tmp + 0.08)) / wp.sin(v2))
    data[tid] = v0
